Posts.Content: I will be having 5th Chemo on Friday (3 fec, 3 t) and haven’t taken temp at all, nurse told me not to bother unless I wasn’t feeling well. Luckily my side effects have been minimal, bit of nausea and constipation for couple of days on fec so haven’t felt the need to take temp
